			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The S-PPU has 8 palettes for backgrounds and 8 palettes for sprites. A palette can be assigned to each 8x8 pixel tile or each sprite. Blending on the S-PPU uses the formula (r1+r2), (r1-r2), or (r1+r2)/2. See <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=12&amp;t=15953" class="postlink">Please consolidate all info</a>.</div>

